Class AccessBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.xekri.leakvm.io.utils.AccessBuilder

  • public final class AccessBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
    AccessBuilder class is a simplify access builder (sticky_bit, owner, group, others) for Read, Write and Execute.
